OL,3,CResidents raise concerns over noise
OL,4,Cand pollution from new quarry
OL,6,FITV Channel reporter Verity Wishart
OL,7,Fspeaks to the residents calling for
OL,8,Fquiet near the new quarry...
OL,10,FGuernsey residents living near the
OL,11,Fheadland at Chouet say a new quarry
OL,12,Fsite is causing significant disruption
OL,13,Fdue to noise and pollution levels.
OL,15,FThe excavation of granite has begun at
OL,16,Fthe new site, the last economically
OL,17,Fviable location for quarrying on the
OL,18,Fisland.
