OL,3,CResidents raise concerns over noise
OL,4,Cand pollution from new quarry
OL,6,FThe company supplying the island's
OL,7,Fconstruction materials, Ronez, has
OL,8,Ffinished excavating stone from Les
OL,9,FVardes which has been in operation
OL,10,Fsince 1961.
OL,12,FPlans were passed in October of 2022
OL,13,Ffor the new site, but concerns were
OL,14,Fraised by nearby residents before its
OL,15,Fapproval regarding the impact on
OL,16,Fbiodiversity, noise levels, and dust.
OL,18,FIt's hoped the nine-acre site at
OL,19,FChouet will extract four million
OL,20,Ftonnes of granite from the headland,
OL,21,Fwhich could take up to 40 years.
