OL,6,FHowever, residents like Sara Woolland
OL,7,Fsay they are sleeping on the other
OL,8,Fside of their house from the quarry to
OL,9,Favoid the noise.
OL,11,FSara explains: "I personally feel it
OL,12,Fis very loud (...) and quite often I
OL,13,Fam woken.
OL,15,F"I know our neighbour up there, her
OL,16,Fhouse is filled with dust, she is much
OL,17,Fnearer and told me some things jumped
OL,18,Foff her shelves
OL,20,Fwith the blast.
