OL,6,F"Certainly when you're in the house, I
OL,7,Ffeel the whole house shake and the
OL,8,Fwindows rattle."
OL,10,FCertain conditions were placed on the
OL,11,Fsite by the Development and Planning
OL,12,FAuthority to address the concerns of
OL,13,Fnearby residents.
OL,15,FThis includes increasing dust traps
OL,16,Fand agreeing on days and times for
OL,17,Fblasting and lowering machinery.
