OL,6,FSteve Roussell, the General Manager at
OL,7,FRonez, says: "We are conscious of our
OL,8,Fneighbours (and) I am pretty confident
OL,9,Fwe can work within the conditions we
OL,10,Fhave been given."
OL,12,F"This was the only o
OL,14,Fption to continue producing stone on
OL,15,Fthe island. The only option would be
OL,16,Fto import the stone which would have a
OL,17,Fsignificant cost.
OL,19,F"Importing stone could be 50% more
OL,20,Fexpensive than locally produced stone."
