OL,6,FPresident for Environment &
OL,7,FInfrastructure, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,8,FSausmarez has been working with
OL,9,Fresidents to mitigate the impact of
OL,10,Fthe quarry and says she "totally
OL,11,Funderstands and emphasises their
OL,12,Fconcerns".
OL,14,FShe adds: "Ultimately the decision the
OL,15,FStates had to make was a strategic one
OL,16,Fabout keeping quarrying on island.
