OL,3,CResidents raise concerns over noise
OL,4,Cand pollution from new quarry
OL,6,F"Some of it is going to be a question
OL,7,Fof seeing how things are when the
OL,8,Fquarry is in operation and there will
OL,9,Fneed to be a certain amount of
OL,10,Fadaptation."
OL,12,FBut some residents say the mitigating
OL,13,Fconditions don't go far enough.
OL,15,FChris Howden has been living on
OL,16,FChouet's headland for 20 years and
OL,17,Fsays more needs to be done to protect
OL,18,Fthe land.
